    h3#external-content External content
    p
        | Sometimes you want to use the collapse plugin to trigger hidden content elsewhere on the page. Because our plugin works on the 
        code.highlighter-rouge id
        |  and 
        code.highlighter-rouge data-target
        |  matching, that’s easily done!
    .bd-example
        .pos-f-t
            #navbarToggleExternalContent.collapse
                .bg-dark.p-4
                    h5.text-white.h4 Collapsed content
                    span.text-muted Toggleable via the navbar brand.
